data.description: Paradise by the Pool Home in South Crestview, Florida. Nestled in a serene cul de sac. Salt Water Pool has undergone upgrades. Backyard presents with an unrivaled blend of modern luxury and natural beauty. Built for entertainment! Upon entering this home, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living space that seamlessly integrates the kitchen, dining, and living areas. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features breakfast bar, like new appliances, and a generous island. Bathed in natural light, the living area boasts a cozy, inviting ambiance for gatherings. Master bedroom is a home of its own.  Masterbath has double vanities, garden tub, walk in shower walk in closets. Formal Dining Space. Come tour today and fall in love!
